<h2>The PDX Social History App</h2>

<h4>Now available on the App Store</h4>

<p>PDX Social History App places all the content of the website on your iPhone, iPad or iPod Touch.</p>

<p>This app includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>audio clips from interviews with a dozen local experts</li>
<li>theme illustrations and historical photos</li>
<li>summary text (in case you forgot your headphones, and don't want to listen out loud)</li>
<li>maps to help you find the historical locations</li>
<li>links to read more about many of these topics</li>
<li>easy ways to share your favorite stories via Facebook, Twitter, email, and text messages</li>
</ul>

